# Surge RULE-SET (ALLOW / WHITELIST)
# Target Policy: DIRECT
# Purpose:
# - Whitelist critical services that must NOT be blocked by reject.list
# - Whitelist Malaysia local services to keep low latency + reduce risk (banking/OTP/government)
#
# Recommended order in Surge [Rule]:
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/allow.list,DIRECT
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/reject.list,REJECT
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/apple.list,DIRECT
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/github.list,Proxy
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/proxy.list,Proxy
#   RULE-SET,https://your-domain-or-raw-link/china.list,DIRECT
#   GEOIP,CN,DIRECT
#   FINAL,Proxy
#
# Notes:
# - Keep this list small and high-value.
# - Prefer DOMAIN for exact hosts, DOMAIN-SUFFIX for whole service domains.
# - Avoid broad TLD rules like DOMAIN-SUFFIX,my.

# -----------------------
# iOS / Apple connectivity (safe, prevents false "no internet")
# -----------------------
DOMAIN,captive.apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,apple.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,icloud.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,push.apple.com

# -----------------------
# Malaysia: Government / national services (common .gov.my / .my)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,gov.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hasil.gov.my

# -----------------------
# Malaysia: Banks / payments (DIRECT recommended; add/remove as you use)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,maybank2u.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,maybank.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cimb.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cimbclicks.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,publicbank.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hongleongconnect.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hlb.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ambank.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bankislam.biz
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,rhbgroup.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bankrakyat.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,bsn.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,affinalways.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,uob.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,ocbc.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,standardchartered.com.my

# DuitNow / PayNet / FPX (Malaysia payment rails)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,paynet.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,fpx.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,duitnow.my

# Touch 'n Go eWallet
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tngdigital.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,touchngo.com.my

# Grab (often used in MY for rides/food/pay)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,grab.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,grabpay.com

# Shopee / Lazada (MY shopping; keep local routing stable)
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,shopee.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,lazada.com.my

# -----------------------
# Malaysia: Telcos / ISP portals (DIRECT)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tm.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,unifi.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,celcom.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,digi.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,maxis.com.my
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,u.com.my

# -----------------------
# Captive portal / Wi-Fi login (generic; add if you often hit captive portals)
# -----------------------
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,hotspot.t-mobile.com

# -----------------------
# Optional: Put PayPal DIRECT here if you want to avoid risk controls
# (If you intentionally proxy PayPal, remove these)
# -----------------------
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,paypal.com
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,paypalobjects.com
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pypl.com
